    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for a functional car at a more accessible price point. The engine and transmission are operational, though you can expect some typical wear and tear associated with its age, such as a slightly noisy idle and the need for a standard tune-up soon. Cosmetically, the exterior shows some visible scratches and a few small dents, while the interior has some minor staining and wear on the upholstery. It is a reliable runner that gets you from A to B, but it is not in showroom condition and will eventually benefit from some cosmetic and mechanical TLC.",
