    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-cared-for 2018 Executive Sport Sedan in a sophisticated Graphite Metallic finish. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and is currently in solid mechanical and aesthetic condition. The exterior paint retains a deep shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor rock chips on the hood and a small hairline scratch near the trunk lid\u2014typical for a car of this age. The 19-inch alloy wheels are wrapped in Michelin Pilot Sport tires with approximately 65% tread remaining. Inside, the cabin features premium Charcoal leather upholstery that remains supple and free of any punctures or unpleasant odors. The power-adjustable seats, dual-zone climate control, and 10.2-inch infotainment system all function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is excellent; it has received synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the most recent multi-point inspection confirmed that the brakes and suspension are in great shape. There are no warning lights on the dash and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. This car comes with a clean title, a full set of floor mats, and two key fobs. It is a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
