    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolute gold to me. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014runs like a dream and has been super well-loved. It's the perfect companion for someone who wants a reliable, stylish car without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s got plenty of life left and is totally ready for its next adventure! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
