    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit features a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. The engine breathes through its signature individual throttle bodies, offering exceptional throttle response and a 7,900 RPM redline. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including a double-VANOS system overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The chassis remains composed with a recently inspected rear subframe and bushings that maintain factory-spec kinematics. A true enthusiast\u2019s specimen that balances raw performance with mechanical integrity.",
